  {
    "key": "854c8dca5354a04507f1d45849894c93c1ebc3807d1e93d2a456af475653a287",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_26.png[/img]%retiredsoldier% sits about the campfire telling war stories. If he's lying, it's merely an embellishment, as the scars all about his body speak unsightly truths. With each tale, the men become more engrossed, emboldened, and ready to get back out there and forge their own stories.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_26.png[/img]%retiredsoldier% sits about the campfire telling war stories. If he's lying, it's merely an embellishment, as the scars all about his body speak unsightly truths. With each tale, the men become more engrossed, emboldened, and ready to get back out there and forge their own stories.\""
